Site_notes: Added in early 2014 to allow additional grid sampling points to be added to the Yeon unit.  The grid was a continuation of the Sunset Beach grid overlay using the same spacing.  From B. Wilkerson, March 2014:  "I just simply continued the eastern line of existing sites in Sunset Beach to the south, placing new points every 350 meters.  I tried to add another line of points south of the western Sunset Beach points, but they all fell on or outside of the Yeon property boundary."
